Useful Links¶

Data¶

  • age_coefficients_and_var.xlsx contains the age polynomial coefficients which can be used to generate the deternministic component of income, and the standard deviation of income - both permenant and transitory income shocks for all 3 education groups - High School Dropouts, High School Graduates, and College Graduates.
  • Conditional Survival Prob Feb 16.xlsx contains the conditional survival probability from age 21 to 100.
